Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:52.09,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Soitsu mitsuke ni yuko ze BOY{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:52.09,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}¡Vamos a salir a buscarlas, muchacho!{\i0}
